# Add feature flag for containerization rollout

Add feature flag to enable gradual rollout of containerization.

## Requirements

- Application config: `containerization_enabled`
- Can be toggled at runtime
- Default to disabled for safe rollout
- Logging when flag is checked

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] `config :pag_server, :containerization_enabled, false` in config
- [ ] `PagServer.Containers.enabled?/0` returns flag state
- [ ] AgentServer checks flag before creating container
- [ ] Flag can be changed at runtime via application env
- [ ] Telemetry event emitted when flag is checked
- [ ] Unit tests for flag behavior
